import photo_1 from "../assets/img/timeline/1.jpeg"
import photo_2 from "../assets/img/timeline/2.jpeg"
import photo_3 from "../assets/img/timeline/3.jpeg"
import photo_4 from "../assets/img/timeline/4.jpeg"
import photo_5 from "../assets/img/timeline/5.jpeg"
import photo_6 from "../assets/img/timeline/6.jpeg"
import photo_7 from "../assets/img/timeline/7.jpeg"
import photo_8 from "../assets/img/timeline/8.jpeg"
import photo_9 from "../assets/img/timeline/9.jpeg"
import photo_10 from "../assets/img/timeline/10.jpeg"
import photo_11 from "../assets/img/timeline/11.jpeg"
import photo_12_1 from "../assets/img/timeline/12-1.jpeg"
import photo_12_2 from "../assets/img/timeline/12-2.jpeg"
import photo_13 from "../assets/img/timeline/13.jpeg"
import photo_14 from "../assets/img/timeline/14.jpeg"
import photo_15 from "../assets/img/timeline/15.jpeg"


export const ourStoryTimeline = [
    {
        index: 0,
        img: photo_1,
        title: "Our First Picture",
        date: "June 22, 2015",
        description: `Our first official date as boyfriend and girlfriend.
            Taken before dinner at Tony D's restaurant in downtown Rochester.`,
    },
    {
        index: 1,
        img: photo_2,
        title: "#1 Fan",
        date: "April 16, 2016",
        description: `Got to know each other and became really close on the RIT campus. Had a long standing bet
        if Nicole scored in her lacrosse game, she would get free Chipotle. Chipotle is always on the mind
        so it was a win-win :)`,
    },
    {
        index: 2,
        img: photo_3,
        title: "Our First Vacation Together",
        date: "June 11, 2016",
        description: `Spent a long weekend exploring Toronto and getting lost in Canada on our
        drive there.`,
    },
    {
        index: 3,
        img: photo_4,
        title: "Halloween Heroes",
        date: "October 29, 2016",
        description: `A tradition was born of amazing couple themed costumes. Vote for Pedro.`,
    },
    {
        index: 4,
        img: photo_15,
        title: "Senior Gala",
        date: "November 18, 2017",
        description: `Celebrated our RIT Senior Gala at the Wintergarden. Who would've thought we'd
        be getting married at the same location 5 years later!`,
    },
    {
        index: 5,
        img: photo_5,
        title: "Graduation",
        date: "May 12, 2018",
        description: `We graduated from RIT together and were anxiously looking forward to moving to New York City to start
        our careers.`,
    },
    {
        index: 6,
        img: photo_6,
        title: "The Last Hoorah",
        date: "July 20, 2018",
        description: `Visited Los Angeles for a week to celebrate one last free Summer before starting our jobs in the Fall.`,
    },
    {
        index: 7,
        img: photo_7,
        title: "Our First Picture in New York City",
        date: "September 16, 2018",
        description: `Our first day of exploring our new city, starting with the High Line in Chelsea.`,
    },
    {
        index: 8,
        img: photo_8,
        title: "Exploring our City",
        date: "November 3, 2018",
        description: `We spent many weekends, like this one in DUMBO, having fun in NYC together.`,
    },
    {
        index: 9,
        img: photo_9,
        title: "Making Friends with the Locals in Aruba",
        date: "September 1, 2019",
        description: `Visited Aruba and spent an amazing week enjoying the beaches, national park and everything
        the Happy Island had to offer.`,
    },
    {
        index: 10,
        img: photo_10,
        title: "ðŸ”¥ Welcome to Flavor Town ðŸ”¥",
        date: "June 6th, 2020",
        description: `Made the best of COVID quarantine birthdays - good thing Girl Fieri was available to make 
        it the best birthday ever.`,
    },
    {
        index: 11,
        img: photo_11,
        title: "Halloween Heroes Strike Again",
        date: "October 31, 2020",
        description: `Dressed up as stages of quarantine; Tiger King and Bread Baking. Carole Baskin killed her husband. (Whacked him)`,
    },
    {
        index: 12,
        multi: true,
        img: photo_12_1,
        title: "Popping the Big Question",
        date: "April 17, 2021",
        description: `On the same spot as our first picture in New York City, we got engaged ðŸ’•`,
    },
    {
        index: 13,
        multi: true,
        img: photo_12_2,
        title: "Still Excited",
        date: "Forever",
        description: `Getting excited to spend the rest of our lives together ðŸ˜Š`,
    },
    {
        index: 14,
        img: photo_13,
        title: "Baby Bagel",
        date: "June 6, 2021",
        description: `We picked up our new baby pup, Bagel, and brought him to his forever home.`,
    },
    {
        index: 15,
        img: photo_14,
        title: "Just the Beginning",
        date: "July 8, 2021",
        description: `Took our engagement pictures in Central Park and had the best time
        celebrating our love. Here's to a lifetime together.`,
    },
]
